  "tipsSheetQuickBookmarksTitle": "Quick Bookmarks",
  "tipsSheetQuickBookmarksDesc": "Long-press the bookmark button on any card to instantly drop a bookmark at your current position without opening the bookmark sheet.",
  "tipsSheetCoverPlayPauseTitle": "Cover Play/Pause",
  "tipsSheetCoverPlayPauseDesc": "Tap the cover art on any card to play or pause. Toggle this in Settings under Absorbing Cards. A faint pause icon shows when playing so you know it's tappable.",
  "tipsSheetFullScreenPlayerTitle": "Full Screen Player",
  "tipsSheetFullScreenPlayerDesc": "Swipe up on any absorbing card to open the full screen player. Swipe down to dismiss it.",
  "tipsSheetQuickAddAbsorbingTitle": "Quick Add to Absorbing",
  "tipsSheetQuickAddAbsorbingDesc": "Swipe right on any book in a list sheet (series, author, search results) to instantly add it to your absorbing queue.",
  "tipsSheetShakeExtendSleepTitle": "Shake to Extend Sleep",
  "tipsSheetShakeExtendSleepDesc": "If you have a sleep timer running and shake your phone, it'll add extra minutes. Configure the amount in Settings under Sleep Timer.",
  "tipsSheetSeriesNavigationTitle": "Series Navigation",
  "tipsSheetSeriesNavigationDesc": "Tap the series name in any book's detail popup to see all books in the series, sorted in reading order with sequence badges on each cover.",
  "tipsSheetSwipeBetweenBooksTitle": "Swipe Between Books",
  "tipsSheetSwipeBetweenBooksDesc": "Swipe left and right on the Absorbing screen to switch between your in-progress books. With Manual queue mode on, the cards also act as your queue, so the next one auto-plays when the current one finishes.",
  "tipsSheetTapToSeekTitle": "Tap to Seek",
  "tipsSheetTapToSeekDesc": "Tap anywhere on the chapter or book progress bar to jump directly to that position. You can also drag the bars for fine-grained control.",
  "tipsSheetSpeedAdjustedTimeTitle": "Speed-Adjusted Time",
  "tipsSheetSpeedAdjustedTimeDesc": "Time remaining and chapter times automatically adjust based on your playback speed. Listening at 1.5x? The time shown reflects how long it'll actually take you.",
  "tipsSheetPlaybackHistoryTitle": "Playback History",
  "tipsSheetPlaybackHistoryDesc": "Tap the History button on any card to see a timeline of every play, pause, seek, and speed change. Tap any event to jump back to that position.",
  "tipsSheetAutoRewindTitle": "Auto-Rewind",
  "tipsSheetAutoRewindDesc": "When you resume after a pause, Absorb automatically rewinds a few seconds so you don't lose your place. The rewind amount scales with how long you were away. Configure it in Settings.",
  "tipsSheetSeriesQueueModeTitle": "Series Queue Mode",
  "tipsSheetSeriesQueueModeDesc": "When you finish a book that's part of a series, Absorb can automatically play the next book. Set queue mode to \"Series\" in Settings.",
  "tipsSheetOfflineModeTitle": "Offline Mode",
  "tipsSheetOfflineModeDesc": "Tap the airplane button on the Absorbing screen to enter offline mode. This stops syncing, saves data, and only shows your downloaded books. Great for flights or low signal areas.",
  "tipsSheetUpcomingReleasesTitle": "Upcoming Releases",
  "tipsSheetUpcomingReleasesDesc": "Open the Library top-right menu to see new and upcoming books across all the series in your library, sorted by release date.",
  "tipsSheetPerBookEqTitle": "Per-Book Equalizer",
  "tipsSheetPerBookEqDesc": "Each book remembers its own equalizer settings. Tweak EQ once for a sci-fi epic and the next time you play it, it sounds the same.",
  "tipsSheetPerBookSpeedTitle": "Per-Book Speed",
  "tipsSheetPerBookSpeedDesc": "Playback speed is saved per book. Run nonfiction at 1.5x and dramatic fiction at 1.0x without setting it every time.",
  "tipsSheetAutoSleepWindowTitle": "Auto Sleep Window",
  "tipsSheetAutoSleepWindowDesc": "Pick the hours you usually fall asleep and the sleep timer will start itself when you begin listening in that window.",
  "tipsSheetSleepFadeChimeTitle": "Sleep Fade and Chime",
  "tipsSheetSleepFadeChimeDesc": "When the sleep timer ends, audio gradually fades out and an optional chime plays so it doesn't cut off mid-sentence.",
  "tipsSheetCarModeTitle": "Car Mode",
  "tipsSheetCarModeDesc": "Tap the car icon to switch to giant-button mode designed for safer use while driving.",
  "tipsSheetAudibleSeriesTitle": "Audible Series Discovery",
  "tipsSheetAudibleSeriesDesc": "Open a series and tap the search icon to pull the full series list from Audible, including missing entries and books you haven't started.",

